, Candidate\u202fB\u2019s technical expertise, stress resilience, and conscientious nature outweigh the communication concerns, making B the strongest overall choice for safe, reliable long\u2011distance operations.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
